## Supabase
SUPABASE_URL="https://YOUR_PROJECT.supabase.co"
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY="YOUR_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY"

## BioTime (reachable from THIS machine)
BIOTIME_BASE_URL="http://192.168.1.50:80"
# Optional override if your endpoint differs
# BIOTIME_TRANSACTION_PATH="/att/api/transactionReport/"

## Optional BioTime auth header
## Examples:
## BIOTIME_AUTH_HEADER="Bearer YOUR_TOKEN"
## BIOTIME_AUTH_HEADER="Basic base64(username:password)"
# BIOTIME_AUTH_HEADER=""

## Optional JSON root hint if BioTime response shape is not auto-detected:
## "array" | "data" | "results"
# BIOTIME_JSON_ROOT="data"

